---
title: BBQ Pork Ribs and Chipotle Potatoes with Tomato and Charred Corn Salad
description: On your plate tonight, succulent, tender BBQ pork ribs are paired with roasted potatoes and onions, feta and a sweet and smoky chipotle mayo drizzle! A mixed green salad with juicy baby tomatoes, charred corn and ranch adds even more bold personality to the meal.
